## Which license should I choose?

**Choose GPL-3.0 if:**
- You are building an open source project
- You can release your derivative work under GPL-3.0
- You are using this for personal/educational purposes

**Choose Commercial License if:**
- You are building a proprietary/closed-source product
- You cannot or do not want to release source code
- You need to distribute this as part of a commercial product
- You require commercial support and warranty
